javadoc: A class that knows how to render {@link CodeUnit}s in 1 or more lines

methods.name: <init>

params.name: location
params.comment: the location of the code unit to display

params.name: codeUnitFormat
params.comment: the format needed to render the code unit

params.name: codeUnitOffset
params.comment:
relative code-unit offset from the specified address 
 		   (this is not a byte-offset, it is expressed in terms of number of code-units).

params.name: codeUnitCount
params.comment: number of code-units to be displayed

methods.name: getDisplayString
methods.comment:
Get the visual representation for the code unit at or containing the address 
 associated with this cell's row

methods.name: getHTMLDisplayString
methods.comment:
Get the visual representation as HTML for the code unit at or containing the 
 address associated with this cell's row

name: CodeUnitTableCellData
comment: A class that knows how to render CodeUnits in 1 or more lines
